         <xsd:enumeration value="PLATFORMITSYSTEM">
            <xsd:annotation>
               <xsd:documentation>A collection of Information technology (IT), both hardware and software, that is physically part of, dedicated to, or essential in real time to the mission performance of special purpose systems within an identified boundary under the control of a single authority and security policy. The systems may be structured by physical proximity or by function, independent of location. (Source CNSSI 4009)</xsd:documentation>
